<h5 id="subject_1093410">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=2609ca61d30f70e2865a0dde3abf860c&amp;topic=122643.msg1093410#msg1093410" rel="nofollow">【Bestiary 1+2】蛇龙（Linnorm）</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_1093410'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_1093410'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong> 于:</strong> 2020-12-31, 周四 16:56:25 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_1093410_quick_mod"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_1093410"><span style="color: maroon;" class="bbc_color"><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">蛇龙（Linnorm）</span></strong></span><br>古老且巨大的蛇龙生活在世界的北部地区，他们憎恨那些自己认定的劣等生物，并试图尽可能对这些不幸的受害者造成更多的痛苦。尽管这些残暴的蛇形生物不如大多数人想象中的带翼真龙强大，但他们确实拥有难以置信且致命的力量，使其可以与真龙的残暴一较高下。<br><br><div class="quoteheader"><div class="topslice_quote">引述: 边栏：额外学识</div></div><blockquote class="bbc_standard_quote"><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>林诺姆之王（LINNORM KINGS）</strong></span></span><br>在林诺姆诸王国哪充满传奇色彩的土地上，斩杀蛇龙是想要宣称王国继承权所需要达成的传统要求。然而，近期登机的林诺姆之王白色艾斯崔德（White Estrid）并非通过杀死蛇龙来宣称王位，而是通过将其打至屈服，并以此获得强大且危险的盟友来巩固她的统治。<br><br><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>死亡诅咒（DEATH CURSES）</strong></span></span><br>蛇龙的死亡诅咒通常都是悲剧传说的主题，而那些认为自己通过斩杀蛇龙来达成英雄伟业的人往往在那之后难逃厄运，不得不屈从于蛇龙死亡之后施加的这顽固诅咒。</blockquote><div class="quotefooter"><div class="botslice_quote"></div></div><br><div class="quoteheader"><div class="topslice_quote">引述: 边栏：关联生物</div></div><blockquote class="bbc_standard_quote"><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>其他蛇龙（OTHER LINNORMS）</strong></span></span><br>除了本节介绍的4种蛇龙之外，蛇龙还有很多种类。枯瘦的石冢蛇龙（Cairn Linnorm）、生有尖刺的寒林蛇龙（taiga linnorm）、水栖的峡湾蛇龙（fjord linnorm）都分别威胁着主物质位面中的某些属于自己的特定地区。</blockquote><div class="quotefooter"><div class="botslice_quote"></div></div><br><div class="quoteheader"><div class="topslice_quote">引述: 边栏：宝藏与奖励</div></div><blockquote class="bbc_standard_quote"><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>蛇龙宝藏（LINNORM TREASURE）</strong></span></span><br>与真龙一样，蛇龙喜欢在巢穴中积累大量的财富。蛇龙的藏品中占较大比重的是那些挑战他们的人的武器、装备和财富，而非铸币或者艺术品。</blockquote><div class="quotefooter"><div class="botslice_quote"></div></div><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>原文</strong></span><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i>原文</i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Linnorm<br>Immense, primeval dragons of the northern reaches of the world, linnorms hate those they deem to be lesser creatures and seek to inflict as much suffering as possible upon their unfortunate victims. While these serpentine monstrosities might not be the powerful winged dragons most imagine, they nonetheless possess incredible strength and deadly powers that often rival authentic dragon brutality<br><br>LINNORM KINGS<br>In the storied Lands of the Linnorm Kings, the slaying of a linnorm is traditionally required for those who would claim a nation’s crown. Recently, though, the Linnorm King White Estrid claimed her crown not by slaying a linnorm but by beating it into submission, gaining a powerful and dangerous ally to help secure her rule.<br><br>DEATH CURSES <br>The death curses of the linnorms are often the subjects of tragic sagas, and those who would think themselves vanquishing heroes for slaying a linnorm often meet their dooms soon thereafter, succumbing to these curses well after the death of the linnorm responsible for bestowing it.<br><br>OTHER LINNORMS<br>Linnorms exist in a variety of forms beyond the four detailed here. The gaunt cairn linnorm, the spiny taiga linnorm, and the aquatic fjord linnorm each terrorize their own specific regions of the Material Plane.<br><br>LINNORM TREASURE<br>As with true dragons, linnorms tend to amass immense piles of treasure in their lairs. These hoards consist of the weapons, gear, and belongings of would-be vanquishers more often than minted coins or works of art.<br></div></div></div></div>
</div>
</div>
