<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_1093414"><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>岩山蛇龙（Tor Linnorm）　　　　生物 21</strong></span></span><br>岩山蛇龙居住在最高的火山中，以自然形成的洞穴或者被融化的火山口为巢。岩山蛇龙的脾气和破坏力就像熔岩本身一样炽热和暴虐。<br><strong><span style="color: orange;" class="bbc_color">罕见</span>　<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">CE</span>　<span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color">巨型</span>　<span style="color: brown;" class="bbc_color">龙类　火　</span></strong><br><strong>察觉</strong>　+37；黑暗视觉（darkvision），60尺灵敏嗅觉（模糊），真视术<br><strong>语言</strong>　邪灵语，龙语，木族语<br><strong>技能</strong>　特技+35，运动+40，隐秘+37<br><strong>力量</strong>　+11，<strong>敏捷</strong>　+8，<strong>体质</strong>　+9，<strong>智力</strong>　-1，<strong>感知</strong>　+8，<strong>魅力</strong>　+9<br><hr /><strong>AC</strong>　47；<strong>强韧</strong>　+38，<strong>反射</strong>　+35，<strong>意志</strong>　+33；对抗魔法时所有豁免+1状态<br><strong>HP</strong>　440，再生20（寒铁使其失效）；<strong>免疫</strong>　诅咒（curse），火焰（fire），麻痹（paralyzed），睡眠（sleep）；<strong>弱点</strong>　寒铁15<br><strong>沸血诅咒</strong>（<span style="color: brown;" class="bbc_color">诅咒 火 原能</span>）　当有生物杀死岩山蛇龙时，他必须成功通过DC 48的意志豁免，失败则会永久性地获得火焰20的弱点，并且由于无时无刻都要忍耐的痛苦中而陷入缓慢1。只要该角色持续承受诅咒带来的痛苦，他的缓慢状态就永远不会低于缓慢1<br><strong>熔岩亲和</strong>　岩山蛇龙能够在浸没于熔岩和岩浆中的情况下自由地呼吸和游泳<br><strong>借机攻击</strong><img src="?PHPSESSID=2609ca61d30f70e2865a0dde3abf860c&amp;action=dlattach;topic=112352.0;attach=89759;image" alt="" height="15" class="bbc_img resized"/>反应　仅限尾扫<br><hr /><strong>速度</strong>　35尺，35尺攀爬，100尺飞行，60尺游泳；行动自如<br><strong>近战</strong><img src="?PHPSESSID=2609ca61d30f70e2865a0dde3abf860c&amp;action=dlattach;topic=112352.0;attach=89756;image" alt="" height="15" class="bbc_img resized"/>单动　啃咬+40（30尺触及，魔法），<strong>伤害</strong>　4d12+19穿刺 外加 岩山蛇龙毒<br><strong>近战</strong><img src="?PHPSESSID=2609ca61d30f70e2865a0dde3abf860c&amp;action=dlattach;topic=112352.0;attach=89756;image" alt="" height="15" class="bbc_img resized"/>单动　爪抓+40（30尺触及，灵巧，魔法），<strong>伤害</strong>　4d8+19挥砍<br><strong>近战</strong><img src="?PHPSESSID=2609ca61d30f70e2865a0dde3abf860c&amp;action=dlattach;topic=112352.0;attach=89756;image" alt="" height="15" class="bbc_img resized"/>单动　尾扫+40（30尺触及，灵巧，魔法），<strong>伤害</strong>　4d6+19钝击 外加 精通攫抓<br><strong>原能内在法术</strong>　DC 44<br>　<strong>常驻9环</strong>　行动自如（freedom of movement）<br>　<strong>常驻8环</strong>　真视术（true seeing）<br><strong>喷吐武器</strong><img src="?PHPSESSID=2609ca61d30f70e2865a0dde3abf860c&amp;action=dlattach;topic=112352.0;attach=89757;image" alt="" height="15" class="bbc_img resized"/>双动（<span style="color: brown;" class="bbc_color">塑能 火 原能</span>）　岩山蛇龙喷出60尺锥形的火焰与灰烬，对区域内的生物造成20d6点火焰伤害（DC 46基础反射豁免）。在岩山蛇龙的下个回合开始时，被喷吐武器影响的区域会被厚厚的灼热烟雾所复盖，同时灼伤眼睛与肺部，对区域内的所有生物造成额外10d6点火焰伤害（DC 46基础反射豁免）。整轮都在烟雾之内且睁着眼睛的生物必须成功通过DC 44的强韧豁免，失败则会目盲1分钟。这些烟雾会在1分钟后消散；在强风（strong winds）中，烟雾会在5轮后消散，在更强的风力影响下，这些烟雾会以更快的速度消散。岩山蛇龙在1d4轮内无法再次使用喷吐武器<br><strong>紧勒</strong><img src="?PHPSESSID=2609ca61d30f70e2865a0dde3abf860c&amp;action=dlattach;topic=112352.0;attach=89756;image" alt="" height="15" class="bbc_img resized"/>单动　3d6+21钝击，DC 46<br><strong>挥舞利爪</strong><img src="?PHPSESSID=2609ca61d30f70e2865a0dde3abf860c&amp;action=dlattach;topic=112352.0;attach=89756;image" alt="" height="15" class="bbc_img resized"/>单动　岩山蛇龙用他的爪抓作出4次打击（Strikes），每次对抗1名不同的目标。这些攻击会被计入岩山蛇龙的多次攻击减值，但是直至岩山蛇龙作出上述所有攻击为止，多次攻击减值的数值不会增加<br><strong>岩山蛇龙毒</strong>（<span style="color: brown;" class="bbc_color">火 伤口 毒素</span>）　<strong>豁免检定</strong>　DC 44强韧；<strong>最大持续时间</strong>　10轮；<strong>阶段1</strong>　8d6火焰伤害和流失1；<strong>阶段2</strong>　12d6火焰伤害和流失2<br><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>原文</strong></span><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i>原文</i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Tor Linnorm<br>Tor linnorms dwell in the tallest volcanic mountains, either within natural formed caverns or within molten craters. A tor linnorm’s temper can be as hot and destructive as the magma the creature resembles.<br>TOR LINNORM CREATURE 21<br>UNCOMMON CE GARGANTUAN DRAGON FIRE<br>Perception +37; darkvision, scent (imprecise) 60 feet, true seeing<br>Languages Aklo, Draconic, Sylvan<br>Skills Acrobatics +35, Athletics +40, Stealth +37<br>Str +11, Dex +8, Con +9, Int –1, Wis +8, Cha +9<br>AC 47; Fort +38, Ref +35, Will +33; +1 status to all saves vs. magic<br>HP 440, regeneration 20 (deactivated by cold iron); Immunities curse, fire, paralyzed, sleep; Weaknesses cold iron 15<br>Curse of Boiling Blood (curse, fire, primal) When a creature slays a tor linnorm, it must succeed at a DC 48 Will save or permanently gain weakness to fire 20 and slowed 1 from the agonizing pain it now endures at all times. As long as a character continues to suffer this curse, its slowed condition can never be reduced below slowed 1.<br>Lava Affinity A tor linnorm can breathe and swim freely while submerged in lava and magma.<br>Attack of Opportunity [reaction] Tail only. <br>Speed 35 feet, climb 35 feet, fly 100 feet, swim 60 feet; freedom of movement<br>Melee [one-action] jaws +40 (reach 30 feet, magical), Damage 4d12+19 piercing plus tor linnorm venom<br>Melee [one-action] claw +40 (reach 30 feet, agile, magical), Damage 4d8+19 slashing<br>Melee [one-action] tail +40 (reach 30 feet, agile, magical), Damage 4d6+19 bludgeoning plus Improved Grab <br>Primal Innate Spells DC 44; Constant (9th) freedom of movement; (8th) true seeing<br>Breath Weapon [two-actions] (evocation, fire, primal) The tor linnorm expels a 60-foot cone of flame and ash dealing 20d6 fire damage to creatures within the area (DC 46 basic Reflex save). At the start of the tor linnorm’s next turn, the area affected by the breath weapon is covered in thick, scorching smoke that burns both the lungs and eyes, dealing an additional 10d6 fire damage to all creatures in the area (DC 46 basic Reflex save). A creature that spends an entire round in the smoke with open eyes must succeed at a DC 44 Fortitude save or is blinded for 1 minute. The smoke dissipates after 1 minute; in strong winds, the smoke dissipates in 5 rounds, and in more powerful winds, it may clear even more quickly. The tor linnorm can’t use Breath Weapon again for 1d4?rounds.<br>Constrict [one-action] 3d6+21 bludgeoning, DC 46<br>Slashing Claws [one-action] A tor linnorm makes four Strikes with its claws, each against a different target. These attacks count toward the tor linnorm’s multiple attack penalty, but the multiple attack penalty doesn’t increase until after the tor linnorm makes all its attacks.<br>Tor Linnorm Venom (fire, injury, poison) Saving Throw DC 44 Fortitude; Maximum Duration 10 rounds; Stage 1 8d6 fire damage and drained 1; Stage 2 12d6 fire damage and drained 2.</div></div></div><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/sCfPsS" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank"><img src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2021/01/04/sCfPsS.png" alt="" class="bbc_img"/></a></div>
