<div class="inner" id="msg_1129479"><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>浅滩蛇龙（Shoal Linnorm）　　　　生物 15</strong></span></span><br>浅滩蛇龙占据了遍布岩石的浅滩海岸线，孤独地沿着岸边蜿蜒而行。尽管他们并不会刻意寻找大型定居点，但这些蛇龙仍旧会袭击由沿海小镇出发的渔民，甚至可能跟随着这些小船返回渔民的家园，评估镇上的防御并制定袭击的计划。浅滩蛇龙倾向于狩猎大型猎物，无论对象是水里游的还是陆上跑。他们喜欢的猎物包含大型乌贼和灰熊——富含脂肪的肉食，而蛇龙会将这些营养代谢成沿着血管流淌的炽热蒸汽。<br><strong><span style="color: brown;" class="bbc_color">罕见</span>　<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">CE</span>　<span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color">巨型</span>　<span style="color: brown;" class="bbc_color">两栖　龙类　</span></strong><br><strong>察觉</strong>　+27；黑暗视觉（darkvision），60尺灵敏嗅觉（模糊），真视术<br><strong>语言</strong>　邪灵语（Aklo），龙语（Draconic），木族语（Sylvan）<br><strong>技能</strong>　特技+28，运动+31，隐秘+28<br><strong>力量</strong>　+8，<strong>敏捷</strong>　+5，<strong>体质</strong>　+7，<strong>智力</strong>　-3，<strong>感知</strong>　+6，<strong>魅力</strong>　+7<br><hr /><strong>AC</strong>　38；<strong>强韧</strong>　+29，<strong>反射</strong>　+25，<strong>意志</strong>　+22；对抗魔法时所有豁免+1状态<br><strong>HP</strong>　295，再生10（寒铁使其失效）；<strong>免疫</strong>　诅咒（curse），火焰（fire），麻痹（paralyzed），睡眠（sleep）；<strong>弱点</strong>　寒铁10<br><strong>溺水诅咒</strong>（<span style="color: brown;" class="bbc_color">诅咒 原能 水</span>）　当有生物杀死浅滩蛇龙时，他必须成功通过DC 38的意志豁免，失败则遭到诅咒。只要溺水诅咒仍在持续着，该角色在饮用任意液体时就必须花费3个动作。尝试更快地饮用液体会导致受害者开始溺水，立即耗尽空气并会失去意识（unconscious）<br><strong>借机攻击</strong><img src="?PHPSESSID=2609ca61d30f70e2865a0dde3abf860c&amp;action=dlattach;topic=112352.0;attach=89759;image" alt="" height="15" class="bbc_img resized"/>反应　仅限尾扫<br><hr /><strong>速度</strong>　35尺，100尺飞行，100尺游泳；行动自如<br><strong>近战</strong><img src="?PHPSESSID=2609ca61d30f70e2865a0dde3abf860c&amp;action=dlattach;topic=112352.0;attach=89756;image" alt="" height="15" class="bbc_img resized"/>单动　啃咬+31（魔法，20尺触及），<strong>伤害</strong>　3d12+16穿刺 外加 浅滩蛇龙毒<br><strong>近战</strong><img src="?PHPSESSID=2609ca61d30f70e2865a0dde3abf860c&amp;action=dlattach;topic=112352.0;attach=89756;image" alt="" height="15" class="bbc_img resized"/>单动　爪抓+31（灵巧，魔法，15尺触及），<strong>伤害</strong>　3d8+16挥砍<br><strong>近战</strong><img src="?PHPSESSID=2609ca61d30f70e2865a0dde3abf860c&amp;action=dlattach;topic=112352.0;attach=89756;image" alt="" height="15" class="bbc_img resized"/>单动　尾扫+31（魔法，25尺触及），<strong>伤害</strong>　4d6+16钝击 外加 精通攫抓<br><strong>原能内在法术</strong>　DC 36<br>　<strong>常驻7环</strong>　行动自如（freedom of movement）<br>　<strong>常驻6环</strong>　真视术（true seeing）<br><strong>喷吐武器</strong><img src="?PHPSESSID=2609ca61d30f70e2865a0dde3abf860c&amp;action=dlattach;topic=112352.0;attach=89757;image" alt="" height="15" class="bbc_img resized"/>双动（<span style="color: brown;" class="bbc_color">塑能 火 原能 水</span>）　浅滩蛇龙喷出滚热的蒸汽，对60尺锥形区域内造成12d8点火焰伤害（DC 36 基础反射豁免）。这些蒸汽会存留至蛇龙的下个回合结束为止；任何人进入此区域或者在此区域开始自身回合时均会承受6d8点火焰伤害（DC 36 反射豁免，通过则无效）。在此期间，由于蒸汽太浓而阻碍了移动以及视线，此区域变为困难地形（difficult terrain）。蒸汽内的所有生物都会进入隐蔽（concealed），所有蒸汽之外的生物对于蒸汽之内的生物也会变为隐蔽状态。浅滩蛇龙在1d4轮内无法再次使用喷吐武器<br><strong>浅滩蛇龙毒</strong>（<span style="color: brown;" class="bbc_color">火 毒素</span>）　<strong>豁免检定</strong>　DC 36强韧；<strong>最大持续时间</strong>　10轮；<strong>阶段1</strong>　4d6火焰伤害和力竭1（1轮）；<strong>阶段2</strong>　6d6火焰伤害和力竭2（1轮）<br><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>原文</strong></span><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i>原文</i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">SHOAL LINNORM<br>Shoal linnorms occupy rocky shoreline shallows and slither along lonely coastlines. While they do not intentionally seek out large settlements, these linnorms nonetheless beleaguer fishers headed out from small coastal towns, and they may even follow skiffs back to their home port to appraise the town’s defenses and plan a raid. Shoal linnorms tend to hunt large prey, both underwater and on land. Their preferred quarries includes giant squid and grizzly bears—meals rich in fat, which the linnorms metabolize into the fiery steam that courses through their veins.<br>SHOAL LINNORM CREATURE 15<br>UNCOMMON CE GARGANTUAN AMPHIBIOUS DRAGON<br>Perception +27; darkvision, scent (imprecise) 60 feet, true seeing<br>Languages Aklo, Draconic, Sylvan<br>Skills Acrobatics +28, Athletics +31, Stealth +28<br>Str +8, Dex +5, Con +7, Int –3, Wis +6, Cha +7<br>AC 38; Fort +29, Ref +25, Will +22; +1 status to all saves vs. magic<br>HP 295, regeneration 10 (deactivated by cold iron); Immunities curse, fire, paralyzed, sleep; Weaknesses cold iron 10<br>Curse of Drowning (curse, primal, water) When a creature slays a shoal linnorm, it must succeed at a DC 38 Will save or become cursed. As long as the curse of drowning persists, the character must spend 3 actions when drinking any liquid. Attempting to drink liquid faster causes the victim to begin drowning, immediately running out of air and falling unconscious.<br>Attack of Opportunity[reaction] Tail only.<br>Speed 35 feet, fly 100 feet, swim 100 feet; freedom of movement<br>Melee [one-action] jaws +31 (magical, reach 20 feet), Damage 3d12+16 piercing plus shoal linnorm venom<br>Melee [one-action] claw +31 (agile, magical, reach 15 feet), Damage 3d8+16 slashing<br>Melee [one-action] tail +31 (magical, reach 25 feet), Damage 4d6+16 bludgeoning plus Improved Grab<br>Primal Innate Spells DC 36; Constant (7th) freedom of movement; (6th) true seeing<br>Breath Weapon [two-actions] (evocation, fire, primal, water) The shoal linnorm exhales scalding steam that deals 12d8 fire damage in a 60-foot cone (DC 36 basic Reflex save). The steam lingers until the end of the linnorm’s next turn; anyone who enters the area or begins their turn in the area takes 6d8 fire damage (DC 36 Reflex save negates). During this time, the steam is so thick that it impedes movement as well as sight, turning the area into difficult terrain. All creatures in the steam become concealed, and all creatures outside the steam become concealed to creatures within it. The shoal linnorm can’t use Breath Weapon again for 1d4 rounds.<br>Shoal Linnorm Venom (fire, poison) Saving Throw DC 36 Fortitude; Maximum Duration 10 rounds; Stage 1 4d6 fire damage and enfeebled 1 (1 round); Stage 2 6d6 fire damage and enfeebled 2 (1 round)<br></div></div></div></div>
</div>
