<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_1129482"><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>寒林蛇龙（Taiga Linnorm）　　　　生物 19</strong></span></span><br>寒林蛇龙体表复盖着数百根形似刚毛且如同长矛一般锋利的黑色尖刺。在蛇龙成群的大陆上生活的博学猎手知道要观察松柏树上卡主的尖刺——这是寒林蛇龙近期曾经经过此地的确切迹象。然而，有时候这种追猎技巧还是不足以避开这些生物；寒林蛇龙就像他的兄弟天池（tarn）和岩山（tor）蛇龙一般，是技能娴熟的追踪者。他们喜欢潜藏在严寒的湿地或沼泽地区中，只把头露出水面，时刻注意着粗心猎物的踪迹。<br><strong><span style="color: brown;" class="bbc_color">罕见</span>　<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">CE</span>　<span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color">巨型</span>　<span style="color: brown;" class="bbc_color">龙类　</span></strong><br><strong>察觉</strong>　+33；黑暗视觉（darkvision），60尺灵敏嗅觉（模糊），真视术<br><strong>语言</strong>　邪灵语（Aklo），龙语（Draconic），木族语（Sylvan）<br><strong>技能</strong>　特技+33，运动+37，隐秘+35<br><strong>力量</strong>　+10，<strong>敏捷</strong>　+6，<strong>体质</strong>　+8，<strong>智力</strong>　-2，<strong>感知</strong>　+6，<strong>魅力</strong>　+7<br><hr /><strong>AC</strong>　44；<strong>强韧</strong>　+35，<strong>反射</strong>　+31，<strong>意志</strong>　+29；对抗魔法时所有豁免+1状态<br><strong>HP</strong>　385，再生15（寒铁使其失效）；<strong>免疫</strong>　诅咒（curse），电击（electricity），麻痹（paralyzed），睡眠（sleep）；<strong>弱点</strong>　寒铁15<br><strong>无尽风暴诅咒</strong>（<span style="color: brown;" class="bbc_color">诅咒 电 原能</span>）　当有生物杀死寒林蛇龙时，他必须成功通过DC 46的意志豁免，失败则会永久获得电击弱点20<br><strong>尖刺</strong>　任何对寒林蛇龙作出近战攻击的生物都会被他的尖刺刺伤，每次攻击承受1d6点穿刺伤害。具有长触及（reach）的近战武器能保护免遭这些尖刺伤害<br><strong>借机攻击</strong><img src="?PHPSESSID=2609ca61d30f70e2865a0dde3abf860c&amp;action=dlattach;topic=112352.0;attach=89759;image" alt="" height="15" class="bbc_img resized"/>反应　仅限尾扫<br><hr /><strong>速度</strong>　40尺，100尺飞行；行动自如<br><strong>近战</strong><img src="?PHPSESSID=2609ca61d30f70e2865a0dde3abf860c&amp;action=dlattach;topic=112352.0;attach=89756;image" alt="" height="15" class="bbc_img resized"/>单动　啃咬+37（魔法，25尺触及），<strong>伤害</strong>　4d12+18穿刺 外加 寒林蛇龙毒<br><strong>近战</strong><img src="?PHPSESSID=2609ca61d30f70e2865a0dde3abf860c&amp;action=dlattach;topic=112352.0;attach=89756;image" alt="" height="15" class="bbc_img resized"/>单动　爪抓+37（灵巧，魔法，25尺触及），<strong>伤害</strong>　4d8+18挥砍<br><strong>近战</strong><img src="?PHPSESSID=2609ca61d30f70e2865a0dde3abf860c&amp;action=dlattach;topic=112352.0;attach=89756;image" alt="" height="15" class="bbc_img resized"/>单动　尾扫+37（灵巧，魔法，30尺触及），<strong>伤害</strong>　5d6+18钝击 外加 精通攫抓<br><strong>原能内在法术</strong>　DC 41<br>　<strong>常驻9环</strong>　行动自如（freedom of movement）<br>　<strong>常驻8环</strong>　真视术（true seeing）<br><strong>喷吐武器</strong><img src="?PHPSESSID=2609ca61d30f70e2865a0dde3abf860c&amp;action=dlattach;topic=112352.0;attach=89757;image" alt="" height="15" class="bbc_img resized"/>双动（<span style="color: brown;" class="bbc_color">电 塑能 原能</span>）　寒林蛇龙对60尺锥形区域喷出带电蒸汽，对区域内的生物造成20d6点电击伤害（DC 41 基础反射豁免）。电雾存续1d4轮，对每名在电雾内结束自身回合的生物造成6d6点电击伤害（DC 41 基础反射豁免）。寒林蛇龙在1d4轮内无法再次使用喷吐武器<br><strong>寒林蛇龙毒</strong>（<span style="color: brown;" class="bbc_color">电 毒素</span>）　<strong>豁免检定</strong>　DC 42强韧；<strong>最大持续时间</strong>　10轮；<strong>阶段1</strong>　7d6电击伤害和流失1（1轮）；<strong>阶段2</strong>　10d6电击伤害和流失2（1轮）<br><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>原文</strong></span><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i>原文</i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">TAIGA LINNORM<br>Taiga linnorms are covered in hundreds of quill-like black spines as sharp as spears. Wise hunters native to linnorm-infested lands know to watch for spines stuck in the bark of conifers—a sure sign that a taiga linnorm has recently passed through. Sometimes this means of tracking isn’t enough to avoid an encounter, however; taiga linnorms, like their tarn and tor brethren, are skilled stalkers. They prefer to lurk in half-frozen bogs or swampy marshlands with their heads poking just above the water’s surface, ever watchful for unwary prey.<br>TAIGA LINNORM CREATURE 19<br>UNCOMMON CE GARGANTUAN DRAGON<br>Perception +33; darkvision, scent (imprecise) 60 feet, true seeing<br>Languages Aklo, Draconic, Sylvan<br>Skills Acrobatics +33, Athletics +37, Stealth +35<br>Str +10, Dex +6, Con +8, Int –2, Wis +6, Cha +7<br>AC 44; Fort +35, Ref +31, Will +29; +1 status to all saves vs. magic<br>HP 385, regeneration 15 (deactivated by cold iron); Immunities curse, electricity, paralyzed, sleep; Weaknesses cold iron 15<br>Curse of Endless Storms (curse, electricity, primal) When a creature slays a taiga linnorm, it must succeed at a DC 46 Will save or permanently gain weakness 20 to electricity.<br>Spines Any creature that makes a melee attack against a taiga linnorm is stabbed by the taiga linnorm’s spines and takes 1d6 piercing damage per attack. A melee weapon with reach protects the user against these spines.<br>Attack of Opportunity[reaction] Tail only.<br>Speed 40 feet, fly 100 feet, swim 50 feet; freedom of movement<br>Melee [one-action] jaws +37 (magical, reach 25 feet), Damage 4d12+18 piercing plus taiga linnorm venom<br>Melee [one-action] claw +37 (agile, magical, reach 25 feet), Damage 4d8+18 slashing<br>Melee [one-action] tail +37 (agile, magical, reach 30 feet), Damage 5d6+18 bludgeoning plus Improved Grab<br>Primal Innate Spells DC 41; Constant (9th) freedom of movement; (8th) true seeing<br>Breath Weapon [two-actions] (electricity, evocation, primal) The taiga linnorm breathes a 60-foot cone of electrified vapor, dealing 20d6 electricity damage to creatures in the area (DC 41 basic Reflex save). The electrified mist persists for 1d4 rounds, dealing 6d6 electricity damage (DC 41 basic Reflex save) to each creature that ends its turn in the mist. The taiga linnorm can’t use Breath Weapon again for 1d4 rounds.<br>Taiga Linnorm Venom (electricity, poison) Saving Throw DC 42 Fortitude; Maximum Duration 10 rounds; Stage 1 7d6 electricity damage and drained 1 (1 round); Stage 2 10d6 electricity damage and drained 2 (1 round)</div></div></div></div>
</div>
